			<text>
				Bruno, the small rat,</text><word>lived, took, read, wrote, drove</word><text>
				lived with his mother in a burrow. Every
				morning,
				his mother went in search of food.
			</text>
		</line>
		<line>
			<text>
				“Bruno, close the door, and</text>
				<word>stay, eat, read, swim, ride</word><text>inside.”Mother rat said as
				usual before
				she went.
			</text>
		</line>
		<line>
			<text>
				Bruno replied, “OK, mom. Bye.”
			</text>
		</line>
